Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.88,0:00:54.02,OP - Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,200)\blur0.753}these trembling feelings are
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.02,0:00:59.17,OP - Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,200)\blur0.753}like whirling petals.
